snippet.textDisplay: The stubbornness and arrogance of one man literally depends on the lives of millions in n. Korea. How can he be so selfish. Just accept the help would be better. You don't have to tell the people where it came from if that makes it any better for rocket man but his people will suffer a lot if he just does nothing.
